Linux cfg80211/nl80211 vendor drop
==================================

This directory is an unrefactored import of Linux 7.0.10 net/wireless.
It is the baseline for bringing Linux cfg80211 and nl80211 behavior into
FeatherCore/NuttX before native cleanup.

Imported source root:

  third/linux-7.0.10/net/wireless

Imported interface headers live under:

  wireless/ieee80211/include

The build switch is CONFIG_WIRELESS_IEEE80211_CFG80211_LINUX and is
disabled by default. Do not expect this tree to compile until the Linux
compatibility layer and the NuttX generic netlink bridge are added.
